<TEXT>
 APRIL 10 _ Israeli commandos kill three senior <ORGANIZATION> PLO </ORGANIZATION> figures in raids on <LOCATION> Beirut </LOCATION>. OCT. 6 _ <LOCATION> Syria </LOCATION> and <LOCATION> Egypt </LOCATION> attack <LOCATION> Israel </LOCATION>. OCT. 22 _ <ORGANIZATION> U.N. </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Security </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Council </ORGANIZATION> adopts Resolution 338, calling for implementation of Resolution 242. NOV. 28 _ <ORGANIZATION> Arab </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> League </ORGANIZATION> endorses <ORGANIZATION> PLO </ORGANIZATION> as sole legitimate representative of <LOCATION> Palestinian </LOCATION> people.
