<HEAD>1982</HEAD>
<TEXT>
 JUNE 6 _ <LOCATION> Israel </LOCATION> invades <LOCATION> Lebanon </LOCATION> for stated purpose of crushing <ORGANIZATION> PLO </ORGANIZATION>, beginning three years of occupation. SEPT. 1 _ <ORGANIZATION> PLO </ORGANIZATION> evacuates <LOCATION> Beirut </LOCATION> and south <LOCATION> Lebanon </LOCATION>. SEPT. 15-17 _ Lebanese Christians allied with <LOCATION> Israel </LOCATION> massacres hundreds of <LOCATION> Palestinians </LOCATION> and Lebanese Moslems in <LOCATION> Beirut </LOCATION>'s <PERSON> Sabra </PERSON> and <LOCATION> Chatilla </LOCATION> refugee camps.
