<HEAD>Michigan Candidate Undermined by Own Governor</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: Updates with later Blanchard comment, inserting new grafs 4-5</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By WILLIAM M. WELCH</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
