ON> is genuinely prepared to live up the far-reaching conditions they have now accepted.'' `` It's a very positive thing,'' said Sen. <PERSON> John </PERSON> <PERSON> Chafee </PERSON>, <LOCATION> R-R.I. </LOCATION> `` There are two parties to the conflict out there, the Israelis and the Palestinians. To not talk to one of the groups is to ignore reality.''
