up 4th pvs, `Dozens of...'</NOTE>
<HEAD>With Israel-PLO, Bjt</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By KARIN LAUB</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>JERUSALEM (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
