 `` <PERSON> Jack </PERSON> <PERSON> Kennedy </PERSON> was a friend of mine. Senator, you're no <PERSON> Jack </PERSON> <PERSON> Kennedy </PERSON>.'' _ Democratic vice presidential candidate <PERSON> Lloyd </PERSON> <PERSON> Bentsen </PERSON> in Oct. 5 debate, after <PERSON> Quayle </PERSON> likened his own experience to the late president's.
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
