</TEXT>
<HEAD>MOST EXPENSIVE TELEVISION PRODUCTION</HEAD>
<TEXT>
 <ORGANIZATION> NBC </ORGANIZATION> spent $ 440 million to broadcast the Summer Olympics.
</TEXT>
<HEAD>HIGHEST PAID ATHLETE</HEAD>
