 <PERSON> Michael </PERSON> <PERSON> Jordan </PERSON> of the <ORGANIZATION> NBA </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Chicago </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Bulls </ORGANIZATION> is making $ 2.7 million, in straight pay, for this season.
