<DATELINE>ATLANTIC CITY, N.J. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
 The price of <ORGANIZATION> Caesars </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> World </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Inc. </ORGANIZATION> stock rose just hours after the company announced that developer <PERSON> Donald </PERSON> <PERSON> Trump </PERSON> had invested in the gaming company. At the close of the day Wednesday on Wall Street, <ORGANIZATION> Caesars </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> World </ORGANIZATION> stock had jumped $ 4.12 -LCB- a share to $ 29.37 -LCB- in consolidated <ORGANIZATION> New </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> York </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Stock </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Exchange </ORGANIZATION> trading. The activity led at least one gaming analyst to credit <PERSON> Trump </PERSON> with being a shrewd investor. `` I take my hat off to <PERSON> Donald </PERSON> <PERSON> Trump </PERSON>,'' said <PERSON> Marvin </PERSON> <PERSON> Roffman </PERSON> of the <LOCATION> Philadelphia </LOCATION> investment firm <ORGANIZATION> Janney </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Montgomery </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Scott </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Inc. </ORGANIZATION> `` It was a wise investment to buy into <PERSON> Caesars </PERSON>. ... We've always felt <PERSON> Caesars </PERSON> was one of the best-managed companies in the industry, and we felt it was worth up to $ 40 a share.'' <PERSON> Trump </PERSON> has asked the federal government for a ruling on whether his investment would violate antitrust laws. He filed notice with the <ORGANIZATION> Justice </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Department </ORGANIZATION> and the <ORGANIZATION> Federal </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Trade </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Commission </ORGANIZATION> of his desire to possibly buy more than 50 percent of <ORGANIZATION> Caesars </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> World </ORGANIZATION> common stock. Although neither <PERSON> Trump </PERSON> nor <ORGANIZATION> Caesars </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> World </ORGANIZATION> will say how much <PERSON> Trump </PERSON> already owns, the filin